WEBVTT

00:00:01.527 --> 00:00:10.853
Hey, good morning family! We're excited to be here today. We're going to do a video together. We want to talk about being thankful.

00:00:10.854 --> 00:00:25.976
It was just on my heart; the Lord told me, 'Brandon, part of the things that the people are believing for manifestation for will come out of being thankful.'This is just where we are, and this is what we practice: walking in thanksgiving.

00:00:25.977 --> 00:00:33.817
I want to get right to the message. We were just talking, and I was trying to make it a casual thing of just what we're thinking about.

00:00:33.818 --> 00:00:41.312
Megan: we're believing for Megan to be healed, for the manifestation of her complete healing.

00:00:41.312 --> 00:00:44.250
We see she's starting to talk a little; words here and there.

00:00:44.251 --> 00:00:48.476
Diana's taught her how to say—what have you been teaching her?

00:00:48.477 --> 00:00:55.563
'In the name of Jesus, I am healed.'Yeah, she goes around and says that all the time. Megan says that now.

00:00:55.564 --> 00:01:01.327
She goes around the house saying, 'In the name of Jesus, I am healed.'And what was the other thing we work on?

00:01:01.328 --> 00:01:21.380
'I have the mind of Christ.'Yep, and Megan walks around—we start, and Megan finishes—'I have the mind of Christ.'We're seeing the manifestations of those scriptures come to pass in her life.

00:01:21.381 --> 00:01:33.036
I'm seeing it in her behavior. I thought if we could just get a little fraction of the Word inside of her, it would change her.

00:01:33.037 --> 00:01:42.052
Diana started trying to help her, and it's been amazing to see God just take a little bit of scripture.

00:01:42.053 --> 00:01:57.359
She doesn't say the whole thing, but 'Christ, Christ.'That's how she started, just saying 'Christ, Christ.'Then I was adding a word every time and I worked with it over weeks and months.

00:01:57.360 --> 00:02:21.484
She's finally got it down now. But she got that down back: 'Christ, mind, Christ.'It's amazing; mind, Christ, mind, Christ. It's prayer coming into fruition.

00:02:21.485 --> 00:02:31.130
It's amazing because, like I said, a lot of people, if you don't see your miracle manifest instantaneously, it's not a miracle for you.

00:02:31.131 --> 00:02:35.637
'Well, God didn't hear me.'But sometimes miracles are gradual.

00:02:35.638 --> 00:02:44.479
Regardless of whether it's gradual and it takes years, or if it takes days, it's still a miracle.

00:02:44.480 --> 00:02:52.336
God is faithful, so you can't give up hope. Sometimes it takes a process.

00:02:52.337 --> 00:03:01.584
I believe with all my heart she's healed now, manifestation now, but we're walking it out. We're not giving up hope.

00:03:01.585 --> 00:03:16.003
I just wanted to encourage you all that even in our life, you might think, 'These people have their stuff all together and they're spiritually so strong.'We're a work in progress just like you all.

00:03:16.004 --> 00:03:31.850
We have a special needs child, and she's been potty trained now—we're grateful—and the Lord is working a miracle in her. It's been a process.

00:03:31.851 --> 00:03:37.423
I believe in God she's going to wake up tomorrow and she's going to talk in full sentences, come on here and tell you all her testimony.

00:03:37.424 --> 00:03:45.340
But right now we're taking baby steps. We're excited. We have the mind of Christ.

00:03:45.341 --> 00:03:53.438
Diana's more working in it, and so we just want to encourage you all today with that miracle.

00:03:53.439 --> 00:04:01.325
Because where she was, folks—I'm telling you—they said she would never talk, she would never have a normal life; they gave up on her.

00:04:01.326 --> 00:04:08.137
Every little thing we rejoice on; we give God all the glory and all the praise.

00:04:08.138 --> 00:04:18.499
It's the biggest deal, even small, tiny things, because that's how you get to the big things: a bunch of little baby steps makes big progress.

00:04:18.500 --> 00:04:33.127
And being thankful for the small things—don't just go, 'Whatever, it's just a small thing.'Like one time I was riding with somebody and the lady at the cash register handed them a free cup of coffee.

00:04:33.128 --> 00:04:45.272
I went, 'Praise God, you just got blessed with a free cup of coffee!'And the person said to me, 'Oh, I don't sweat the small things.'I went, 'Hold on a minute.

00:04:45.273 --> 00:04:54.851
If you don't rejoice over the small things, you won't rejoice over the big things either.'You've got to grasp a hold of even a small cup of coffee.

00:04:54.852 --> 00:05:02.310
You've got to get excited when God blesses you with five cents.

00:05:02.311 --> 00:05:13.259
You can't say, 'I'll be excited when I get a million dollars.'If you can't get excited over the dollar—come on, folks—we've got to be grateful for everything.

00:05:13.260 --> 00:05:21.954
And that's what I'm trying to get across: it's being grateful.

00:05:21.955 --> 00:05:32.799
I have to go back to even when I was telling you I'm believing for a house, believing for this, believing for that—being thankful for what He's already given you.

00:05:32.800 --> 00:05:44.638
There are times I murmur and complain in my heart and I get upset about things; you murmur and complain, you whine about it, and I have to stop.

00:05:44.639 --> 00:05:53.831
'Father, just thank You. Thank You that today we had a meal. Thank You, Father, that You provided lights for my home.

00:05:53.832 --> 00:06:03.291
Thank You, Lord, that I have a YouTube channel. Thank You, Father, that these people even come on here and even want to listen to me.'It's humbling.

00:06:03.292 --> 00:06:15.977
'Lord, thank You for all the kind words they give me. I know, Lord, it's not me, it's all You, and I give You all the glory for it.'But they tune in, and I'm thankful for every single one of them.

00:06:15.978 --> 00:06:21.378
It's very interesting just taking and being grateful for the small things.

00:06:21.379 --> 00:06:27.821
You may think, 'I don't have anything to be grateful for,'but you say, 'I'm thankful for the air that I breathe.

00:06:27.822 --> 00:06:40.282
I'm thankful for my sight. I'm thankful I have ears.'Find something in your life today to give God praise for.

00:06:40.283 --> 00:06:49.507
Be grateful that you have life, the opportunity that you woke up this morning to breathe.

00:06:49.508 --> 00:06:57.466
You may be in pain, but something might not hurt. Maybe your toe doesn't hurt.

00:06:57.467 --> 00:07:08.754
'Thank You, Father, my toe doesn't hurt. It could be cut off. Thank You, I have a toe. Thank You, I have an earlobe.

00:07:08.755 --> 00:07:20.190
Thank You, Father, I have an eyebrow.'Find something to give Him praise for today regardless of how bad you think you've got it.

00:07:20.191 --> 00:07:37.435
It doesn't matter how small you think it is; it's big to God. God's a good God and He deserves all our praise.

00:07:37.436 --> 00:07:44.187
Even if it's for a star you find in the sky: 'God, I thank You for that star right there.

00:07:44.188 --> 00:07:48.291
Thank You, Father, for that star. I thank You for the tires on my car.

00:07:48.292 --> 00:07:54.720
I thank You for the dirt I walked on today.'If you don't have anything else to be thankful for, thank Him for something.

00:07:54.721 --> 00:08:08.734
Amen. When you start doing that, you'll start seeing miracles manifest in your life. You'll start seeing outpourings of the Spirit of God.

00:08:08.735 --> 00:08:16.681
God's looking for a heart who's perfect towards Him, and that is a grateful heart, a cheerful heart, a heart that's full of joy and thankfulness.

00:08:16.682 --> 00:08:33.691
It isn't easy to do it all the time. I have to catch myself and go back; I get in my prayer time and I go, 'Oh God, I'm sorry. I've been fussy today, had a bad attitude today.

00:08:33.692 --> 00:08:49.537
I shouldn't have been so ungrateful for what You have.'He'll tell me, 'Brandon, really, what's your problem?'I'll say, 'Well, I'm irritated about this and this.'He says, 'But I've given you so much.

00:08:49.538 --> 00:08:56.854
I've blessed you so much. Why can't you take time to thank Me for that?'When the Lord asks you that...

00:08:56.855 --> 00:09:08.728
'God, forgive me. Forgive me, Lord.'You want to crawl underneath a rock. We all have our issues.

00:09:08.729 --> 00:09:15.554
But I'm just trying to tell y'all something that we have to do with Megan, and we're thanking Him for this.

00:09:15.555 --> 00:09:22.410
It's a big deal to us. You understand what I'm saying? You live it with me.

00:09:22.411 --> 00:09:52.224
Yeah, you're stirring me up. It's so good. It's time to be more thankful. I feel His presence. Thank You, Lord.

00:09:52.225 --> 00:10:05.928
I don't want to just always come on here and preach to y'all; I just want to tell y'all—just being real—just being grateful will do a lot in your life.

00:10:05.929 --> 00:10:22.548
I know it seems like some days are really hard, but what I'm telling you right now works, for He inhabits the praise of His people, and when praises go up, blessings come down.

00:10:22.549 --> 00:10:30.799
If you take your eyes off of yourself... I even heard this when I traveled with Benny Hinn.

00:10:30.800 --> 00:10:37.398
When we'd go in the back room and we'd pray for the people in the back—if they took their eyes off of begging God...

00:10:37.399 --> 00:10:43.504
if you're begging, you're not believing. If you're begging God for your miracle, you're not believing.

00:10:43.505 --> 00:10:50.829
When you take your eyes off of yourself and you start praying for somebody else, that is usually when the manifestations start coming quickly.

00:10:50.830 --> 00:11:03.854
When you're consumed with yourself, worried about 'I'm dying, stage four cancer, I only have a couple of days to live, I've got to have a miracle right now,'He knows what you need.

00:11:03.855 --> 00:11:25.396
But when they took their focus off of their need and started focusing on praying for other people's needs, their manifestation instantaneously came.

00:11:25.397 --> 00:11:35.313
Those miracles were real. When I ushered, I'm telling you, the manifestations of the glory of God...

00:11:35.314 --> 00:11:44.514
I've never felt them in a meeting like I did whenever I was with Benny Hinn. I was an anointing junkie.

00:11:44.515 --> 00:11:53.948
I met Diana at a Bible study, but we started going to Benny Hinn services and traveling when we first got married, ushering and helping out.

00:11:53.949 --> 00:12:12.905
We had our own needs, barely making it financially, but we were hungry and desperate. I learned a lot.

00:12:12.906 --> 00:12:30.359
If you think you can achieve something by trying to be self-righteous—God can't stand self-righteousness. It is nasty to Him.

00:12:30.360 --> 00:12:39.042
So you've got to know that it's by grace you're saved through faith, and any miracle you ever get from God is because of His grace.

00:12:39.043 --> 00:12:47.203
His mercy is new every morning and great is His faithfulness to His children.

00:12:47.204 --> 00:12:56.572
You can't achieve righteousness because He's the one that does it all; He paid the price for you.

00:12:56.572 --> 00:13:14.113
Thank You, Jesus. Don't give up on what you're believing for.

00:13:14.114 --> 00:13:32.799
He said to me, 'Son, remember the video you just did about believing Me for big things in 2024? A lot of my kids already have given up on it.

00:13:32.800 --> 00:13:52.232
You're only four weeks into the year and they've already given up on their dream.'I want you to brush it off, blow it off, dust it off—it's only four weeks old—and believe Him again.

00:13:52.233 --> 00:13:59.936
Touch that hem of His garment. Believing for your house, believing for your spouse, believing for your miracle.

00:13:59.937 --> 00:14:20.976
God has a plan for your life. Latch onto it like the woman with the issue of blood.

00:14:20.977 --> 00:14:52.735
Say, 'I'm not letting go of this until I get my miracle.'Part of it is being thankful for what you have.

00:14:52.736 --> 00:15:03.071
I felt it in my heart to finish this off today to tell you all: God loves you, and we love you.

00:15:03.072 --> 00:15:14.590
We pray for you all the time. Diana gets behind the computer and reads your emails.

00:15:14.591 --> 00:15:29.799
We take it very seriously—this gift what God's given us, our congregation.

00:15:29.800 --> 00:15:42.017
When you want to bless us with finances, we pray for your money; we pray for harvest, for abundance, for new jobs, creative ideas to get wealth.

00:15:42.018 --> 00:15:52.202
We believe in the supernatural in this household. God shows up and shows off.

00:15:52.203 --> 00:15:59.414
He is ruling and reigning inside of you. Good things are ahead for you if you believe.

00:15:59.415 --> 00:16:21.533
2024 will be a good year for you. What are you believing for? What are you thankful for? My wife, my kids, my health.

00:16:21.534 --> 00:16:37.868
Even when I'm overcoming something, I'm thankful, 'Father, You've healed me.'I thank You, Father, that You've set me free from obesity.

00:16:37.869 --> 00:17:08.660
Greater is He that is in me than he that is in the world! Click the like button, the subscribe button, and our notification bell.

00:17:08.661 --> 00:17:29.701
It helps us get the Gospel out. It's the algorithm. When you do that, the Gospel is spreading throughout the whole world.

00:17:29.702 --> 00:17:45.607
Africa, Australia, Europe, Japan, China—this channel is touching their lives.

00:17:45.608 --> 00:17:54.534
People getting born again, people turning from homosexuality to give their heart to Jesus, wayward children coming home.

00:17:54.535 --> 00:18:20.135
People are getting healed, delivered from demonic spirits.

00:18:20.136 --> 00:18:28.669
It's because of you all clicking that like button. We don't take any one of you all for granted.

00:18:28.670 --> 00:19:30.269
God bless y'all. Let's pray real quick. 'Father, we thank You for every single person who's part of this YouTube channel.

00:19:30.270 --> 00:19:49.556
Diana and I agree in the name of Jesus that they are blessed from the top of their head to the soles of their feet.

00:19:49.557 --> 00:20:03.476
You said in Your Word that You'd meet all their needs, and I thank You, God, that You're a faithful God and You bring that harvest to them now.

00:20:03.477 --> 00:20:23.970
Thank You, Lord, for jobs and better jobs. Thank You, Lord, for food for their homes and for their bills being paid.

00:20:23.971 --> 00:20:38.836
But Lord, I thank You for the overflow, that they're living in abundance to the extreme, that they've got so much they're able to help the people around them.

00:20:38.837 --> 00:21:14.963
We're a funnel, a pitcher to pour out and help everybody else. Lord, I thank You for creative ideas to get wealth.

00:21:14.964 --> 00:21:18.518
But Lord, I thank You that they may need healing in their body.

00:21:18.519 --> 00:21:30.793
You paid the price for that too. By Your stripes we are healed.

00:21:30.794 --> 00:21:38.399
I speak healing and wholeness over their bodies today in the name of Jesus.

00:21:38.400 --> 00:21:55.759
Throats be healed. Congestion and viruses, be gone. Deliverance over their bodies.

00:21:55.760 --> 00:22:04.241
Oh, somebody needs new... I just saw it... something going on with your blood.

00:22:04.242 --> 00:22:11.105
I speak healing over your blood right now. It's leukemia. The Lord said leukemia.

00:22:11.106 --> 00:22:22.670
I curse leukemia right now in the name of Jesus and we call it to go now.

00:22:22.671 --> 00:22:53.978
Healing belongs to you. You're not underneath the curse. God doesn't teach people through sickness and disease.

00:22:53.979 --> 00:23:00.495
The Bible says He comes that you might have life more abundantly.

00:23:00.496 --> 00:23:12.559
He doesn't have sickness in heaven, so He can't give it to you.

00:23:12.560 --> 00:23:51.816
The devil comes to kill, steal, and destroy. He took all infirmities so that you don't have to have them.

00:23:51.817 --> 00:24:14.333
Jesus paid it for you. Sow a seed, believing for a manifestation of healing.

00:24:14.334 --> 00:24:37.382
Father, I take authority over leukemia right now. Get out of their body right now in Jesus'name.

00:24:37.383 --> 00:24:51.297
We call them healed and whole and well. Lord, anybody else that needs a miracle, You have made and paid the way.

00:24:51.298 --> 00:24:58.636
We consider it done. We call them healed from the top of their head to the soles of their feet.

00:24:58.637 --> 00:25:14.786
God, You fixed it all. If you got a miracle today, comment down below.

00:25:14.787 --> 00:25:56.912
Tell the people. We are excited for you. Jesus loves you so much and we love you. See you next time. Have a blessed and wonderful day. Bye!'

